data.description: Beautiful home in Phase One of Walk at East Village 55 plus community. Shows like a model-94k of upgrades including extra trim including crown and chair rail custom shutters. First floor master. Walk in tiled showers in all 3 baths. Ceiling fans in every bedroom, gas fireplace in the Living room. Large center island and SS appliances in kitchen. 2 car garage. Community features a clubhouse for activities, pool, bocce ball. Hand-scraped HW floors throughout the home! Extra storage, Custom bookshelves in the Living room. Seller will pay first year of HOA for buyer!
